OL,3,CPlans for more politicians in the
OL,4,CSenedd passed
OL,6,FPlans to change the size of the and
OL,7,Fthe way that it's elected have been
OL,8,Fbacked by in a crucial vote which was
OL,9,Fthe last chance that members had to
OL,10,Falter those plans.
OL,12,FThe changes as set out in the (Members
OL,13,Fand Elections) Bill will be rubber-
OL,14,Fstamped in a vote next Wednesday and
OL,15,Fwill be introduced in time for the
OL,16,Fnext Welsh election in 2026.
