OL,3,CPlans for more politicians in the
OL,4,CSenedd passed
OL,6,FSupporters say that more are needed
OL,7,Fbecause the Welsh Parliament has more
OL,8,Flaw-making power than when it was
OL,9,Ffirst created and the Welsh Government
OL,10,Fneeds more scrutiny. Opponents say
OL,11,Fit's a waste of money creating more
OL,12,Fpoliticians.
OL,14,FAnd the way they're elected would
OL,15,Fchange. Currently we choose 40 from
OL,16,Fconstituencies and 20 from a "top-up"
OL,17,Flist. The new system would see 16 new
OL,18,F"super constituencies" each with six
OL,19,FSenedd members.
