OL,4,CSenedd passed
OL,6,FYou wouldn't vote for an individual,
OL,7,Fyou'd vote for a political party and
OL,8,Fthe winners would be chosen from lists
OL,9,Fthat the parties provide.
OL,11,FSupporters say that's fairer and would
OL,12,Freflect the votes all parties won.
OL,13,FOpponents say it would destroy the
OL,14,Flink between voters and the person
OL,15,Frepresenting them.
