OL,6,FMr Price said that he was pleased to
OL,7,Fhear the consensus and didn't want to
OL,8,F"fracture that consensus" so didn't
OL,9,Fpush for a vote on his amendment.
OL,11,FAnother opposition idea met with cross-
OL,12,Fparty support and won a promise from
OL,13,Fthe Welsh Government to look at
OL,14,Fanother way of making it reality.
OL,16,FThe Conservatives had proposed what's
OL,17,Fknown as a recall system - a way of
OL,18,Fallowing voters to remove Senedd
OL,19,Fmembers between elections if they're
OL,20,Ffound to have done wrong.
