OL,7,Fthe principle and so the Tories
OL,8,Fwithdrew their amendment in order to
OL,9,Fstart working towards a recall system
OL,10,Fusing other Senedd procedures.
OL,12,FWhere tempers flared was when the
OL,13,FConservatives tried to amend the Bill
OL,14,Fto require a referendum to be held
OL,15,Fbefore the changes are brought in.
