OL,6,FThat brought a rare intervention from
OL,7,Fthe former First Minister Mark
OL,8,FDrakeford who said that "Let me just
OL,9,Fassure the Member that the fact that
OL,10,Fhe doesn't recall something is no
OL,11,Fevidence of it not having happened.
OL,13,F"Time after time during the election I
OL,14,Fmade it clear in interviews, in
OL,15,Fbroadcasts, in debates that my party
OL,16,Fstood for a reform of this Senedd
OL,17,Falong the lines that are now in front
OL,18,Fof it. No referendum of any sort is
OL,19,Frequired."
